title: Locarno Agreement
new-page: true
subtitle: Stresemann's Big Win
view-if: year = 1925 and month = 10
max-visits: 1
tags: event

= Locarno Agreement

The Locarno Conference has ended in partial, but important, success. Stresemann and Luther managed to persuade the Allies to accept many of the nationalist demands that Schiele had proposed, although they were unable to get a strong commitment regarding implementation dates. However, Schiele and the German Nationalists are outraged that the treaty implies, in their view, a renunciation of western border changes. They are demanding that Luther issue a public letter stating that the treaty would allow peaceful border adjustments on the grounds of popular sovereignty. Luther's proposed private letter was sufficient for Schiele but not for the DNVP Reichstag delegation who have declared they will pull out of the cabinet which would cost us our majority. If we want the Luther cabinet to survive and pass these treaties we must either win the toleration of the DNVP or the SPD.

- @new_elections: Good riddance, let's call new elections.
- @spd_support: Good riddance, let's ask the SPD for support
- @dnvp_toleration: Let's ask the DNVP for toleration
- @give_up: Then let's give up on the treaty

@new_elections
title: Good riddance, let's call new elections.
call: set_next_election_time
on-arrival: rural_dnvp -= 3; new_middle_dnvp -= 1; workers_dnvp -= 1; old_middle_dvp += 1; new_middle_dvp += 3; old_middle_wp += 3; ddp_regionalist_dissent += 10; ddp_left_bourgeois_dissent += 5; dnvp_relation -= 15; dvp_relation -= 10; z_relation -= 5; spd_relation += 1; nationalism -= 2
go-to: root

@spd_support
title: Good riddance, let's ask the SPD for support
on-arrival: {!
// TODO: Later route this through the proper cabinet/minister selection system.
Q.chancellor = "Luther";
Q.spd_in_government = 0;
Q.spd_toleration = 1;
Q.in_minority_government = 1;
Q.minority_government = 1;
Q.z_in_government = 1;
Q.dvp_in_government = 1;
Q.dnvp_in_government = 0;
Q.rural_dnvp -= 1;
Q.old_middle_dnvp += 2;
Q.old_middle_dvp -= 2;
Q.old_middle_wp += 5;
Q.new_middle_wp += 3;
Q.old_middle_ddp -= 2;
Q.workers_spd += 1;
Q.ddp_regionalist_dissent += 10;
Q.ddp_left_bourgeois_dissent += 5;
Q.dnvp_relation -= 20;
Q.dvp_relation -= 10;
Q.spd_relation += 5;
Q.nationalism -= 4;
!}
go-to: root

@dnvp_toleration
title: Let's ask the DNVP for toleration
# TODO: Implement the full Locarno Agreement effects for asking the DNVP for toleration in a later pass.
on-arrival: resources += 0
go-to: root

@give_up
title: Then let's give up on the treaty
choose-if: 0
unavailable-subtitle: Are we crazy?
